OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,FA woman was stranded on a crowded
OL,8,Ftrain for more than 11 hours with
OL,9,Flimited facilities, after Spain's
OL,10,Fpower cut disrupted its railways.
OL,12,FLarge parts of Spain and Portugal were
OL,13,Fhit by major power outages on Monday,
OL,14,Fcausing chaos at airports and train
OL,15,Fstations and shutting off traffic
OL,16,Flights.
