OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,FAngelica had set off from Madrid on
OL,8,FMonday, heading for the northeastern
OL,9,Fcity of Zaragoza, when the train
OL,10,Fsuddenly lost power, leaving her and
OL,11,Fhundreds of others stuck in the middle
OL,12,Fof nowhere.
OL,14,FAngelica told ITV News: "I mean, it's
OL,15,Fno one's fault, no one could predict
OL,16,Fthat. So we cannot blame anyone. But
OL,17,Fit was quite rough because, like, when
OL,18,Fwe were in the middle of the field in
OL,19,Fthat train.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
