OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,F"It was really hard because the
OL,8,Ftoilets were closed, because it was a
OL,9,Fmess. Like, everyone was really
OL,10,Fchaotic. So we had to go to the toilet
OL,11,Foutside and, you know, they provided
OL,12,Fus with water and they were also
OL,13,Fgiving sandwiches.
OL,15,F"But it was not enough, so we didn't
OL,16,Fget any. You know, the priority was
OL,17,Fkids and elders."
OL,19,FAfter her ordeal, Angelica finally
OL,20,Fmade it to Barcelona-Sants station on
OL,21,FTuesday.
