OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,FAnother passenger, Godwin Emmanuel,
OL,8,Fhadn't taken a holiday in five years
OL,9,Fbecause of work pressures, but just as
OL,10,Fhe was about to set off for a few days
OL,11,Fin Malaga, the power went out.
OL,13,F"I've not been on holiday for the past
OL,14,Ffive years," Godwin told ITV News at
OL,15,FBarcelona-Sants station. "This is my
OL,16,Ffirst holiday, just for four days,
OL,17,Fbecause I'm autonomous, I work hard
OL,18,Fall day,"
OL,20,F"(I just wanted to be) free to breathe
OL,21,Fa little bit, you know."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
