OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,FHe added that he has gone "through
OL,8,Fhell" and is demanding compensation
OL,9,Ffor the delays he suffered.
OL,11,FHe explained: "I'm trying to get
OL,12,Fcompensation after all this, you know,
OL,13,Fwe're going through hell standing here
OL,14,Fall day.
OL,16,F"This is really bad for everyone...
OL,17,FThey should compensate us, everyone,
OL,18,Ffor what they put us through. At the
OL,19,Fend of the day, the transport system,
OL,20,Fthey make a hell of a lot of money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
