OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,F"They have billions. They can
OL,8,Fcompensate everyone. Probably they're
OL,9,Fgoing to get something from the
OL,10,Fgovernment for the destruction of
OL,11,Ftheir business. But they need to
OL,12,Fcompensate everyone, every one of us."
OL,14,FYosra was travelling from Barcelona to
OL,15,FMadrid on Monday, en route to Mexico,
OL,16,Fwhen the power outage hit.
OL,18,FShe missed her flight and had to spend
OL,19,Fthe night at the Barcelona-Sants
OL,20,Fstation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
