OL,3,C'Chaotic': Woman trapped on train for
OL,4,C11 hours amid Spain's widespread power
OL,5,Ccut
OL,7,F"They cancelled all the trains, and I
OL,8,Fhad to sleep here. I had to pass the
OL,9,Fwhole night here in the station," she
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,F"And now we are supposed to go to take
OL,13,Four new ticket, supposedly, but we
OL,14,Fdon't have any information yet. We
OL,15,Fdon't know if we will go today or if
OL,16,Fwe have to stay another night here.
OL,18,FWhen asked if she is tired due to the
OL,19,Ffatigue of travelling, she responded,
OL,20,F"Yes, I am".
